    "body": "I am getting same issue when trying to run a sandboxed development build of my electron application - why is electron wanting access to com.apple.GameController.gamecontrollerd entitlement?\r\n\r\nI'm seeing the following sandbox violations:\r\n`deny(1) mach-lookup com.apple.GameController.gamecontrollerd`\r\n`deny(1) network-bind /private/var/folders/tc/ywjttcf564xdt9mswdddbx6c0000gn/T/MY_APP/S/SS`\r\n`deny(1) file-read-data /`\r\n`deny(1) nvram-get BSD Name`\r\n\r\n\r\nElectron: 1.6.11\r\nElectron-builder: 19.7.1\r\nOSX: 10.12.5"
  },
